articles.description: In her set, Mo'Nique, 54, called Hughley, 59, out by name, as she felt slighted she wasn't the clear headlining act for The Comedy Explosion show.
articles.content:
D.L. Hughley has hit back at Mo'Nique after the comedienne complained that she was supposed to be the headlining act at a comedy gig in Detroit.
